data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2.5-bath home in Ohatchee School District. Enjoy modern living with a farmhouse sink, subway tile, stainless steel appliances, and updated light fixtures. The LVP flooring adds elegance, complemented by a 1-car garage. Situated on 1.5 acres of flat, cleared land for outdoor activities. Welcome to your dream home!  Since listing the 2nd Master bathroom has been updated with new paint, new vanity, and new light fixtures. Also the porch railing has been rejuvenated with new railing and paint.
